        .col-md-4
          .row.text-content.text-left
            %h4.important-content or are just looking for new ones?
            %ul 
              %li One Platform for all Workshops
              %li Huge diversity of choices
              %li Save time
              %li Connect
              %li Enjoy
            %h4 Read more...
        .col-md-4
          .row.text-content.text-left
            %h4.important-content or just want to connect, inspire and embrace
            %ul
              %li Experience matters
              %li Everybody has unique skills
            %h4 Read more...
  .row.row-centered
    %section.darkgrey
      %h2.section-heading How it works
      .col-sm-6.col-sm-offset-3
        #switch-slides.btn-group.btn-group-justified
          .btn-group
            %button#learn_click.btn.btn-default.btn-lg.btn-block.active{"data-toggle" => "button", :type => "button"} Learn
          .btn-group
            %button#offer_click.btn.btn-default.btn-lg.btn-block{:type => "button"} Offer
      #learn-slide.col-sm-10.col-sm-offset-1.switch-slide
        %p Learn a Skill
      #offer-slide.col-sm-10.col-sm-offset-1.switch-slide
        %p Share a Skill, Offer a workshop
